This is an UNOFFICIAL GraalVM native-image build of the opendataloader-pdf CLI.
It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or supported by the opendataloader
project or Hancom Inc.

This product bundles and redistributes a compiled form of:

  opendataloader-pdf
  Copyright 2025-2026 Hancom Inc.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
  https://github.com/opendataloader-project/opendataloader-pdf

The opendataloader-pdf shaded JAR (and therefore the native binary built from
it) includes third-party components under their respective licenses; their
LICENSE/NOTICE files are retained inside the JAR's META-INF and carried into the
binary. Notable components include Apache PDFBox/FontBox, veraPDF, Jackson,
OkHttp/Okio, Kotlin stdlib, and Apache Commons CLI.

No source code of opendataloader-pdf is modified or redistributed by this
repository; the build fetches the published artifact (via the pip wheel) and
compiles it ahead-of-time with GraalVM native-image.
